{"id":150777,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/汇市分析-欧元兑美元下跌超过2/","date":"2011-05-08T10:00:29Z","modified":"2011-05-08T10:00:29Z","title":"[汇市分析] 欧元兑美元下跌超过2%","content":"<p><span></span></p>\n<div>欧</div>\n<p>元兑美元周四下跌超过2%，因对全球经济放缓的担忧和大宗商品价格下跌促使投资者纷纷逃离高风险货币。</p>\n<p>电子交易系统显示，欧元从周三尾盘的1.4827美元跌至1.4518美元，2%的跌幅也是2010年8月份以来的最大单日百分比跌幅。</p>\n<p></p>\n<div><span><img border=\"0\" height=\"10\" src=\"http://cn.wsj.com/gb/img/more_arrows.gif\" width=\"5\" /> 本文涉及股票或公司</span></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><b><a href=\"http://cn.wsj.com/gb/stocksearch.asp?KeyWord=CADAY&#038;chinesename=&#038;englishname=Top%20Canadian%20Stories&#038;country=&#038;exchange=&#038;symbol=\" rel=\"nofollow\">Top Canadian Stories</a></b></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/2MOLRqUjFXFdyFQ3nvqL_XYKIEY/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/2MOLRqUjFXFdyFQ3nvqL_XYKIEY/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/2MOLRqUjFXFdyFQ3nvqL_XYKIEY/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/2MOLRqUjFXFdyFQ3nvqL_XYKIEY/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wsjfeature/~4/-52SH5Q-MDs\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}